main event: Two objects with bright lights, round in shape, appeared to start blinking and disappeared to the north in a straight line while hovering, observed for 1 minute.
interesting points: The objects seemed to blink or flash during the sighting.
Additional data was requested from the observer, but was not received, so the case was closed as insufficient data.
The sighting occurred in Duncanville, Texas on November 9, 1963.
The objects were described as being round in shape with bright lights.
The objects moved in a straight line while hovering before disappearing to the north.
sighted object: Two round objects with bright lights
